    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to clarify a \"social consensus\" regarding gender identity, specifically probing if opposition to progressive school policies is based on \"real\" evidence or if it is merely \"people being difficult.\" The assistant responds by framing the scientific side as being based on established findings and the opposing side as being driven by \"entrenched social or ideological beliefs.\"",
